description: Galanga is serving up our nation’s capitol with the worldly flavors of Indonesian cuisine and D.C. is delighted. The robust Beef and Chicken Redang will keep you reordering, and you’ll find yourself craving their perfectly cooked jasmine rice that soothingly cools the heat of the  scrumptiously spicy Balado Shrimp. If you see this distinctive bamboo-lined truck on the street, you'll know you’re in for a deliciously authentic experience!
name: Galanga
